# Fix UI Issues — Loading Animations, Save Version, and Saving State

## Identified Issues

### Issue 1: Static Loading Spinners 🔴
**Root cause:** All `Loader2` icons use `animation: 'spin 1s linear infinite'` but **`@keyframes spin` is not defined** in [globals.css](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Desktop/structured-questionnaire-answering-tool/src/app/globals.css). The spinner renders but never rotates.

**Affected pages:** Dashboard (loading projects), Project (save button, export button, generate button), History (loading versions).

### Issue 2: Save Version Not Working 🔴
**Root cause:** Needs investigation via browser network tab — the API route logic at `/api/versions` POST looks correct. Possible causes:
- `answer_versions` table column mismatch (`saved_at` vs `created_at`)
- RLS policy blocking inserts
- Empty questionnaires list causing empty snapshot

### Issue 3: No Visual Lock During Save
**Current state:** `isUIFrozen` correctly disables buttons, but there's no **visual overlay** or status indicator showing the user that saving is in progress.

### Issue 4: Loading Skeleton is Plain
The loading state is just a static icon + text — no shimmer/pulse animation to indicate activity.

---

## Proposed Changes

### Global Styles

#### [MODIFY] [globals.css](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Desktop/structured-questionnaire-answering-tool/src/app/globals.css)
- Add `@keyframes spin { from { transform: rotate(0deg); } to { transform: rotate(360deg); } }`
- Add `@keyframes pulse` for loading skeletons

---

### Dashboard

#### [MODIFY] [dashboard/page.tsx](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Desktop/structured-questionnaire-answering-tool/src/app/dashboard/page.tsx)
- Replace static loading text with animated skeleton cards (pulsing placeholder cards)
- Ensure spinner actually spins after keyframes fix

---

### Project Workspace

#### [MODIFY] [project/[id]/page.tsx](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Desktop/structured-questionnaire-answering-tool/src/app/project/%5Bid%5D/page.tsx)
- Add a **floating status bar** at top-right during save (e.g., "⏳ Saving version...") with animated spinner
- Replace plain loading with animated skeleton layout
- Improve [handleSaveVersion](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Desktop/structured-questionnaire-answering-tool/src/app/project/%5Bid%5D/page.tsx#133-142) error logging to help diagnose failures

---

### Versions API

#### [MODIFY] [api/versions/route.ts](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Desktop/structured-questionnaire-answering-tool/src/app/api/versions/route.ts)
- Add detailed error logging for each DB step
- Return error details in response for debugging

